OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1777997460
OL,3,CTwelve fire crews tackle huge blaze at
OL,4,CWarburtons site
OL,6,FFirefighters from Lancashire Fire and
OL,7,FRescue Service are tackling a huge
OL,8,Ffire at an industrial site in Burnley.
OL,10,FCrews were called to the Warburtons
OL,11,Fsite on Billington Road at 14:45 on
OL,12,FMonday 4 May, with 12 fire engines
OL,13,Fattending the site. Locals are being
OL,14,Furged to keep windows and doors closed.
OL,16,FThe scene was captured from the air by
OL,17,F'Bank of Dave' star Dave Fishwick who
OL,18,Fcircled the area in his helicopter.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
