OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1777997460
OL,3,CTwelve fire crews tackle huge blaze at
OL,4,CWarburtons site
OL,6,FIn a video posted on social media he
OL,7,Fis heard to say: "I hope everybody is
OL,8,FOK. There is a huge fire just down
OL,9,Fthere. It's unbelievable how big the
OL,10,Ffire is.
OL,12,F"I'm calling the fire brigade now to
OL,13,Fmake sure they know about it. The big
OL,14,Fbig factory roof is going up
OL,16,F"It looks like it's Warburtons going
OL,17,Fup in flames."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
