PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1777997460
OL,3,CTwelve fire crews tackle huge blaze at
OL,4,CWarburtons site
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Warburtons has
OL,7,Fconfirmed in a statement that it is
OL,8,Fthe affected site: "We can confirm
OL,9,Fthat thankfully everyone has safely
OL,10,Fbeen evacuated from the building.
OL,12,F"We are grateful to the fire brigade
OL,13,Fwho are currently working extremely
OL,14,Fhard to get the fire under control.
OL,16,F"We don't know the cause of the fire,
OL,17,For the full extent of the damage as
OL,18,Fyet. "
